@Lucias, After you've installed it from the .iso file that you got from extracting, you'll need to download one additional file that will allow your game to run without needing Steam to verify it.

http://thepiratebay.sx/torrent/8300453/BioShock_Infinite_Crack_Only-FLT

Download that and replace the files that it gives you with the ones in your install directory.
